WEBVTT

00:00:01.579 --> 00:00:03.329
Ono što radite,

00:00:03.329 --> 00:00:06.121
sada, baš u ovom trenutku,

00:00:06.121 --> 00:00:08.163
vas ubija.

00:00:08.163 --> 00:00:10.913
Više nego auti ili internet

00:00:10.913 --> 00:00:13.663
ili čak oni mali mobilni uređaji o kojima pričamo,

00:00:13.663 --> 00:00:16.579
tehologija, koju koristite gotovo svakodnevno

00:00:16.579 --> 00:00:19.788
je ova, vaša guza.

00:00:19.788 --> 00:00:22.913
Ovih dana ljudi sjede 9,3 sata dnevno,

00:00:22.913 --> 00:00:26.413
što je više nego što spavamo, 7,7 sati.

00:00:26.413 --> 00:00:28.288
Sjedenje tako snažno prevladava,

00:00:28.288 --> 00:00:30.246
da čak ne preispitiujemo koliko to radimo,